# Keep docker build contexts small and avoid copying pnpm symlinked node_modules
# (which point outside the build context and would break COPY). Image deps are
# installed inside the Dockerfile instead.
**/node_modules
.git
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
tests/e2e/test-results
deploy/kind/web-console/dist
deploy/kind/credentials.env
deploy/kind/tls
**/*.log
